"About Remodex" = "关于 Remodex";
"Done" = "完成";
"Control **Codex** from your iPhone." = "从 iPhone 控制 **Codex**。";
"Your Mac runs a lightweight **bridge** that connects to a **relay server** over WebSocket." = "你的 Mac 运行一个轻量级 **bridge**，通过 WebSocket 连接到 **relay server**。";
"A lightweight WebSocket server that routes messages between your iPhone and your Mac." = "一个轻量级 WebSocket 服务器，用于在 iPhone 和 Mac 之间转发消息。";
"You can **self-host** the relay on your own VPS, or use the default hosted endpoint from the npm package." = "你可以在自己的 VPS 上 **自托管** 中继，也可以使用 npm 包默认提供的托管端点。";
"The bridge spawns a **`codex app-server`** process — the same JSON-RPC interface behind the Codex desktop app and IDE extensions." = "bridge 会启动一个 **`codex app-server`** 进程，也就是 Codex 桌面应用和 IDE 扩展背后的同一套 JSON-RPC 接口。";
"On first connect, the bridge prints a **QR code** containing:" = "首次连接时，bridge 会打印一个包含以下信息的 **二维码**：";
"Scan it once from this app. After the handshake:" = "用这个 App 扫描一次。握手完成后：";
"The QR remains available as a recovery path if trust changes or the session can't be resolved." = "如果信任状态变化或无法解析会话，二维码仍可作为恢复路径使用。";
"After pairing, every message is wrapped in encrypted envelopes:" = "配对后，每条消息都会封装在加密信封中：";
"The bridge handles **git commands** from your phone locally on the Mac:" = "bridge 会在 Mac 本地处理来自手机的 **git 命令**：";
"Also supports **workspace revert** — preview and apply reverse patches when the assistant makes changes you want to undo." = "同时支持 **工作区回退**：当 assistant 做了你想撤销的修改时，可以预览并应用反向补丁。";
"Threads from your phone are persisted as JSONL rollout files, so they appear in **Codex.app** on your Mac." = "手机上的会话会以 JSONL rollout 文件持久化，因此会出现在 Mac 的 **Codex.app** 中。";
